Package: laserize
Type: Package
Title: Obtain LASER text emebeddings by itnerfacing the Python laserembeddings module.
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Hauke", "Licht", email = "hauke.licht@uzh.ch", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The pacakge provides an R interface to the sentence embeding functionality
    provided by the laserembeddings Python module.
    It projects texts from different languages in the same, multilingual embedding space.
